{"tid":2382586,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"雷射筆射向馬鞍山警署 女侍應被控受審","createTime":"2021-01-27T11:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T14:22:53.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"22eab57afdab5a16aa099491665a0842fc0c2052","tid":2382586,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"前年8月10日大埔反修例遊行，晚上演變成多區快閃，有示威者包圍馬鞍山警署。其間31歲女侍應被指以雷射筆照射警員，事隔近半年遭起訴管有攻擊性武器罪，案件今於沙田裁判法院審訊。辯方指出，<span class=\"red\">被告承認當日有使用過雷射筆射向馬鞍山警署，但對照射到警員以至距離上有所爭議。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">警長34962陳振球</span>接受盤問時表示，受雷射光照射後「嗰下唔舒服流眼水」，但仍繼續工作，直至任務完成後才去看醫生。辯方從片段中指出，女被告射出<span class=\"red\">光束僅只三秒</span>，並非警長所稱的五秒綠色光束，其間亦曾發出藍白色光束，而光束上下左右搖擺，警長同意。<br />\n<br />\n彭官向辯方指出，控罪並非襲警罪，而是管有攻擊性武器罪，提示辯方不要混淆。<span class=\"red\">辯方指出爭議點在於被告沒有意圖。</span>"},{"pid":"94fab4dfd0f105de164930c5d67a7f703a9e1dc0","tid":2382586,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T11:10:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/XGUOF3VYORDTLELC2R2LR3SBSQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2FXGUOF3VYORDTLELC2R2LR3SBSQ%2F&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdnwaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=93239977\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2FXGUOF3VYORDTLELC2R2LR3SBSQ%2F&h=2ee5e63a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/XGUOF3VYORDTLELC2R2LR3SBSQ/</a>"},{"pid":"dd25cbb9a106c8c2fdb1f91c6954cdf21611eed9","tid":2382586,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T11:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bdaa4581e08972e3536a52ef286bca4821d4e11","tid":2382586,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T11:13:30.